  "profile": "realistic",
  "adversarial": false,
  "intent": "A full CIS RHEL10 audit ruleset (catalog #19): identity watches, an auid-narrowed execve, rare time/mount syscalls, a sudo-log watch, and the -e 2 finalize. The broad realistic case on el10 (audit 4.0.3). Mixed byte constants.",
